		</form></span></div></div></div><div class="topper-basic__border_bottom"></div></div><div class="info-box" style="background-color:#faeadc"><div class="info-box__content"><div class="info-box__body"><p></p><p>The FT-Nikkei Investing in America ranking is a snapshot of the best US cities for foreign multinationals to do business. This report looks at the biggest challenges facing overseas investors in the US, how the winning cities are pulling in more deals — and why the laggards are falling behind. <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://www.ft.com/content/61014f7b-0507-4450-9d58-8fa992883c9a"><strong>Read more</strong></a> on how we calculated the FT-Nikkei Investing in America ranking.</p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="container container--w-div flow-row"><div class="container__item flow-ln-1 LX:flow-ln-2"><div class="graphic--flourish"><figure><a href="#visualisation/15264818" data-asset-type="flourish" data-flourish-id="visualisation/15264818"><div id="visualisation/15264818" class="graphic--flourish-disclaimer o-message o-message--alert o-message--neutral" data-o-message-close="false" data-o-component="o-message" style="background-color:#f2dfce"><div class="o-message__container"><div class="o-message__content"><p class="o-message__content-main">An interactive graphic failed to load. This is most likely due to being offline or JavaScript being disabled in your browser.</p></div></div></div></a></figure></div></div><div class="container__item flow-ln-1 align-self--center LX:flow-ln-2"><div class="content-link-centred"><div class="content-link-centred__heading js-teaser-headline" data-content-id="f676aff0-b439-4e53-8adc-a737471ce701"><a data-trackable="heading-link" href="https://ig.ft.com/us-cities-index">The best US cities for international business</a></div><p class="content-link-centred__standfirst"><a href="https://ig.ft.com/us-cities-index" data-trackable="standfirst-link">The Financial Times and Nikkei looked at over thre